  <!-- Síntesis de la actividad -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="synthesis-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Display the first, fourth, and fifth figures.</li>
      <li>
        <q>¿Cómo recubrieron cada figura?</q>  (I filled the whole figure with tiles until I couldn’t fit any more. I started with the bottom row, then made the row above it until the figure was full.)
      </li>
      <li>
        <q>¿Cómo encontraron el área de cada figura?</q>  (I counted the number of tiles it took to fill each figure completely.)
      </li>
      <li>Consider asking, 
        <q>¿De cuáles figuras les pareció más fácil encontrar su área?</q>  (The rectangle, because there were clear rows and columns. The third one, because we could split it into 2 rectangles. All of them, because they could all be covered completely with square tiles and had no uncovered space.)
      </li>
      <li>
        <q>¿Por qué fue importante no dejar ningún espacio al recubrir sus figuras?</q>  (Because the whole figure needs to be completely covered. If there are gaps between tiles or around the edge, then the whole figure isn’t covered.)
      </li>
    </ul>
  </paragraphs>


